answers.answer: Congratulations how many weeks we're you?
My gosh, if only all labor was like yours! That must have been nice! Congratulations!
Congrats you make it sound so easy... well enjoy ur new bundle of joy.
Oh wow I hope mine will be that easy! :) Congratulations and best wishes.

I was 39 weeks 2 days. I was given Cervidil tuesday evening...and was supposed to have pitocin wednesday morning. She came really fast and contractions were very painful. I was asking for an epidural when she checked me it was too late she was born 3mins later. My water broke during the second to last contraction and then I pushed ...she was ready I guess. I was shocked at her size with having gestational diabetes.  She is healthy and we are doing good.Not sure whats better slow less painful labor or hard PAINFUL fast labor
